name: QualityNet
overview:
Quality Net has magnificently developed as a market trailblazer in the fields of Satellite Based Communication. Our strong vision of ensuring internet accessibility in Afghanistan makes us optimal for all internet users in Afghanistan. Our comprehensive knowledge of in-demand technologies and strong vision of customer goals allows us to execute tailored services that meet or exceed customer requirements and needs.

Quality Net has always focused on the advanced application of VSAT technology. Over this period we have remained an active customer-focused organization that provides our customers with the most vastly proficient engineers and technical personnel in the industry. We present ourselves as the premium provider of Internet and all sorts of Communication Services across Afghanistan.
